data.description: ***$5000 in closing cost!  ***The mix of amenities and location highlights make this property seem like a great choice for a spacious and modern living experience.  Some of the standout features of this home located in Cypress Point in Schertz Texas:  5 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms   3089 sq. ft  2 car garage .  Offering ample space.  Primary bedroom downstairs with a large walk-in closet, walk in shower with large garden tub and double vanities.  Providing convenience and privacy.  Study/office:  A dedicated space for work or personal projects. Formal dining room. Game room and media room: Perfect for entertainment and relaxation.  Open floor plan with vaulted ceiling in the family room with fireplace.  Creating an open and airy atmosphere. Spacious backyard  for entertainment and privacy (home backs up to farmland) and balcony in front.  Ideal for outdoor activities and gatherings.  Comal District Schools.  Proximity to various attractions and necessities:  IH 35, Randolph AFB, shopping, dining, and natural attractions like the Guadalupe River.  Overall, this home  offers a balanced combination of practicality, comfort, and entertainment options.
